# CI/CD Workflows

## Build & Test

- `.github/workflows/dotnet.yml`
- Builds `AiImage.Core` and `AiImageApi`
- Skips MAUI HybridApp (Linux runner)
- Runs unit tests

## MAUI Windows Build

- `.github/workflows/maui.yml`
- Runs on `windows-latest`
- Builds `AiImage.HybridApp` â†’ `.msix`
- Manual trigger only

## MAUI Android Build

- `.github/workflows/maui-android.yml`
- Runs on `ubuntu-latest`
- Builds `.apk` for Android
- Manual trigger or push to main

## Auto Versioning

- `.github/workflows/versioning.yml`
- Updates `csproj` versions from Git tags + commit count
- Applied to Core, API, HybridApp
